From JEK Subject Bernadette dates Joe Moore writes Mary at that time appeared to a girl named Bernadette at She referred to herself as the Immaculate Since a nine year old would have no way of knowing about the doctrine the apparition was deemed to be true and it sealed the case for the Bernadette was years old when she had her visions in four years after the dogma had been officially proclaimed by the Yours James Kiefer